  "2026-03-07T22:41:42.118Z",maintainer-agent,"Planned change-set: update PRD and README first to document snake_case aliases for --acceptance_criteria and --estimated_minutes in create/update contracts, then wire commander option aliases and normalization, then add integration/release-contract assertions."
  "2026-03-07T22:42:09.312Z",maintainer-agent,"Docs-first update complete: PRD.md and README.md now declare snake_case aliases --acceptance_criteria and --estimated_minutes for create/update flag contracts before runtime implementation."
  "2026-03-07T22:44:57.400Z",maintainer-agent,Initial pm test run exposed Commander alias limitations when three long flags were declared on one option. Reworked create/update alias registration to separate --estimated_minutes options and retained required create validation in normalizeCreateOptions.
  "2026-03-07T22:57:55.046Z",maintainer-agent,"Implemented docs-first snake_case alias parity: PRD/README now document --estimated_minutes and --acceptance_criteria for create/update contracts; CLI wiring in src/cli/main.ts now accepts these aliases via dedicated option registration plus normalization fallbacks; integration and release-readiness contract tests now cover alias runtime/help/doc behavior."
